text: Brian Williams (14 September 1936 – 19 January 2010) was a former Australian rules footballer who played with Fitzroy in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * * Category:1936 births Category:2010 deaths Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Fitzroy Football Club players Category:Camperdown Football Club players
